---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import conceptImg from '../../assets/shop-interior.png'
---

<section class="concept section" aria-labelledby="concept-heading">
  <div class="container concept__grid">
    
    <div class="concept__content">
      <span class="eyebrow gsap-fade">Promesa y Concepto</span>
      <h2 id="concept-heading" class="gsap-up">
        Ingeniería de imagen <br />
        <em style="color:var(--color-gold);font-style:italic">basada en morfología</em>
      </h2>
      <span class="gold-line gsap-fade"></span>
      <div class="concept__text gsap-up">
        <p>
          En Jaime Corcho no creemos en los cortes de catálogo. Creemos en la 
          arquitectura del rostro. Cada servicio comienza con un análisis profundo 
          de tus facciones para diseñar un resultado que no solo te haga lucir bien, 
          sino que proyecte tu verdadera identidad.
        </p>
        <p>
          Nuestra promesa es simple: precisión técnica absoluta en un entorno 
          de exclusividad diseñado para el hombre moderno.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="concept__features">
        <div class="concept__feature gsap-up">
          <div class="concept__feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 7h-9m9 4h-6m6 4H10M4 17l6-6-6-6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>Análisis Facial</strong>
            <span>Diseño basado en tus rasgos únicos</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="concept__feature gsap-up">
          <div class="concept__feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>Exclusividad</strong>
            <span>Atención 1 a 1 sin prisas</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="concept__image gsap-right">
      <div class="concept__image-frame">
        <Image 
          src={conceptImg} 
          alt="Concepto de barbería premium Jaime Corcho" 
          class="concept__img"
          width={600}
          height={800}
        />
        <div class="concept__image-accent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.concept__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
  gap: 6rem;
  align-items: center;
}

.concept__text p {
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}

.concept__features {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 2rem;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}
.concept__feature {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 1rem;
}
.concept__feature-icon {
  width: 3rem;
  height: 3rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: var(--color-gold);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.concept__feature strong {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-white);
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.concept__feature span {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--color-gray);
}

.concept__image {
  position: relative;
}
.concept__image-frame {
  position: relative;
  aspect-ratio: 4/5;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  padding: 1rem;
}
.concept__img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}
.concept__image-accent {
  position: absolute;
  top: -2rem;
  right: -2rem;
  width: 8rem;
  height: 8rem;
  border: 2px solid var(--color-gold);
  z-index: -1;
  opacity: 0.5;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .concept__grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }
  .concept__image {
    order: -1;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .concept__features {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
</style>

<script>
import { gsap } from 'gsap'
import { ScrollTrigger } from 'gsap/ScrollTrigger'

gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger)

gsap.utils.toArray<HTMLElement>('.concept .gsap-up').forEach((el) => {
  gsap.from(el, {
    y: 40,
    opacity: 0,
    duration: 0.8,
    ease: 'power3.out',
    scrollTrigger: {
      trigger: el,
      start: 'top 85%',
    }
  })
})

gsap.from('.concept__img', {
  scale: 1.1,
  opacity: 0,
  duration: 1.2,
  ease: 'power3.out',
  scrollTrigger: {
    trigger: '.concept__image',
    start: 'top 80%',
  }
})
</script>
